name: contradictory 1
description:
*This photo is from the "World of Contradiction" photo collection.

*in this photo, more attention is paid to the fact that heaven is a place where man is involved in no contradictions.
And he sees good and evil as one thing and is not in conflict
Where there is no time and place and everything is in unity
Where man is at peace with the world

*"World of Contradiction photo collection" refers to the fact that in this world in which we live, everything in it finds meaning with its contrast.
And if there is a day
Because there is night, otherwise it had no meaning
And if there is good because there is evil
And if we understand love because we suffer for it.
